@startuml
title face-analyzer - AWS Lambda (MediaPipe Face Landmarker 표정 분석)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #F3E5F5
  BorderColor #8E24AA
}
skinparam component<<storage>> {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #607D8B
}
skinparam component<<layer>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
  BorderColor #FBC02D
}
skinparam component<<external>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #FB8C00
}
skinparam queue {
  BackgroundColor #F3E5F5
  BorderColor #8E24AA
}

component "frame_extractor Lambda\n(영상 → 1FPS .jpg)" as FrEx <<external>>
queue "SQS\nmefit-face-trigger\n(가시성 300s, 배치=1)" as TriggerQ
database "S3\nvideo-frame-files\n({sessionUuid}/{turnId}/frames/)" as S3In <<storage>>
queue "SQS\nvideo-step-complete" as DoneQ
component "Backend\nCelery SQS Worker" as BE <<external>>

package "face-analyzer/" {
  package "layers/" {
    component "face-analysis\n(MediaPipe 0.10.14 +\nOpenCV headless +\nNumPy + Pillow +\nProtobuf, strip 후 ~250MB)" as Lmed <<layer>>
    component "mefit-video-common\n(공유 Layer:\nS3 client / SQS publisher /\nLogger / Config)" as Lcommon <<layer>>
  }

  package "functions/face_analyzer/" {
    component "handler.py\nLambda entry\n메모리=1024MB · timeout=5m\nx86_64 / Python 3.12" as Func
  }

  package "analyzer/ (로직 모듈)" {
    component "face_detector\nMediaPipe FaceLandmarker\n+ blendshape + head pose" as Det
    component "frame_analyzer\n단일 프레임 분류 +\n저장 최적화" as FrA
    component "emotion_category\n5 score → positive/\nnegative/neutral 임계값" as EmCat
    component "batch_processor\nS3 객체 순차 분석\nlocal 폴더 분석" as Batch
    component "statistics\n분포 / 평균 /\n표정 전이율 집계" as Stat
  }

  database "models/\nface_landmarker.task\n(3.7 MB)" as Models <<storage>>
}

' 트리거 흐름
FrEx --> TriggerQ : SendMessage\n{frameBucket, framePrefix,\n sessionUuid, turnId}
TriggerQ --> Func : SQS Event Source\n(Records[0].body)

' 내부 처리
Func --> Batch : analyze_s3_images()
Batch --> S3In : list_objects_v2\n+ get_object (.jpg)
Batch --> FrA : per-frame 분석
FrA --> Det : analyze_face()
Det ..> Models : load (Lazy init,\n콜드 스타트 1회)
FrA --> EmCat : classify_expression()
Batch --> Stat : compute_statistics()
Stat --> Func : 통합 JSON 결과

' Layer 의존
Func ..> Lcommon
Func ..> Lmed
Det ..> Lmed
FrA ..> Lmed

' 결과 영속화
Func --> S3In : put_object\nface_analysis_result.json
Func --> DoneQ : publish_step_complete\n(step=face_analyzer)
DoneQ --> BE : kombu polling

note bottom of EmCat
  멘토 피드백:
  표정 분류 정확도는 본질적으로 제한적
  → positive / negative / neutral / no_face
     거시 카테고리로 단순화
  → 임계값 기반(임계값 5개) 결정론적 분류
  → 동양인 무표정 보정 (eye_squint 보조 판정)
end note

note right of Det
  MediaPipe Face Landmarker:
  - 478 facial landmarks
  - 52 blendshape coefficients
  - head pose (yaw/pitch/roll)

  추출 핵심 5 score:
  smile, frown, brow_down,
  jaw_open, eye_squint
end note

footer face-analyzer/ — MediaPipe Face Landmarker · 임계값 기반 분류 · SQS 트리거 · S3 결과 영속화
@enduml
